# Internal sprint planning — paybot-mcp is Apache-2.0 public; story files
# may reference operator-private workspace slugs and must not ship by default.
# Use `docs/stories/*` (not `docs/stories/`) so individual files can be
# re-included via negation patterns below. Git docs: "It is not possible to
# re-include a file if a parent directory of that file is excluded."
docs/stories/*
# Carve-out: bank-pitch sprint stories ARE tracked (no operator-private
# content; co-located with their specs under docs/specs/BP-*/).
# Vetted on a per-file basis before commit by @sm + @po + boundary audit.
!docs/stories/BP-1.6-commit-staged-mcp-work.md
!docs/stories/BP-1.6/
docs/stories/BP-1.6/*
!docs/stories/BP-1.6/semantic-intent.md
!docs/stories/BP-1.6/semantic-mapping.md
!docs/stories/BP-3.1-hitl-middleware.md
!docs/stories/BP-3.1/
docs/stories/BP-3.1/*
!docs/stories/BP-3.1/semantic-intent.md
!docs/stories/BP-3.1/semantic-mapping.md
!docs/stories/EPIC-BANK-PITCH-2026-06-30.md

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AIOX secret-hygiene hardening — added 2026-05-22 by @devops
# Per operator directive (public-repo exposure prevention).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Environment files (extra)
.envrc
.direnv/

# Secret stores — cert + key material
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cer
*.crt
*.der
secrets/
secrets.json
credentials.json
credentials/
.credentials/

# Provider-specific token files
.npmrc
.yarnrc
.yarnrc.yml
!.yarnrc.example
.netrc
.aws/
.gcp/
service-account*.json
gcp-key*.json
*-sa.json
firebase-debug.log

# Local config that often holds secrets
config.local.*
config.*.local
local.config.*
*.local.json
*.local.yaml
*.local.yml

# IDE secrets
.vscode/settings.local.json
.idea/dataSources.local.xml
.idea/dataSources.xml
.idea/sqldialects.xml

# OS / editor temp that can hold pasted secrets
*.bak
*.tmp
*.swp

# AI/agent tool dumps that may include conversation w/ keys
.aiox/handoffs/*.yaml
!.aiox/handoffs/LATEST.md
.claude/settings.local.json

# Build artifacts that might inline secrets at build time
.next/cache/**
dist-local/
